OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPublic emergency message   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freleased ahead of UK test  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Further details have been released     
OL,6, about the alert that will be sent to   
OL,7, smartphones across the UK next week, to
OL,8, test a new public warning system.      
OL,10,FA message with a siren at 15:00 BST on 
OL,11,F23 April will say "in a real emergency,
OL,12,Ffollow the instructions in the alert to
OL,13,Fkeep yourself and others safe".        
OL,15,FIt will give a sound and vibration for 
OL,16,F10 seconds even for phones on silent.  
OL,18,FPhone users will have to acknowledge   
OL,19,Fthe alert before they can continue     
OL,20,Fusing their devices.                   
